    <item>
      <title>随着FX紧缩磨损，埃及通货膨胀率略为一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/egyptian-inflation-plunges-by-almost-half-as-fx-crunch-wears-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及的通货膨胀率在2月份下降了几乎一半，这是外国货币紧缩的影响，该货币紧缩的效果每年以美元的价格以美元为食。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/egyptian-inflation-plunges-by-almost-half-as-fx-crunch-wears-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 07:47:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
